-------- DANGERZONE LIVE CD -------- 
 
This is a live CD of dangerzone-rust 
- 'doas' is installed instead of 'sudo', the general usage is similar 
- Standard service management: systemctl <action> dangerzone-httpserver 
- The relevant binaries are in /usr/local/bin 
- By default the server binds to 0.0.0.0 on port 13000 
- By default internet connectivity is forbidden 
  - As root, run 'dangerzone-fw-disable' to allow internet access 
  - As root, run 'dangerzone-fw-enable' to restore firewall rules

